omer service department via email - <a href="mailto:cs@unitedspb.com">cs@unitedspb.com</a> or call <a href="tel:1-800-233-6956">800-233-6956</a> and we will gladly assist you!</li></ol><p class="subtextdisclaimer"><span style="font-size: small;"><em>*Please Note That the Initial Shipping Cost Will NOT be Refunded*</em></span></p><br><h2>EXCHANGE PROCESS</h2><ol><li>Every order that is shipped from our warehouse should come with a prepaid shipping label and a packing slip included on the inside of the box, mailer or envelope.</li><li>Please place your item either in the original packaging or in a similar dimension container and apply the shipping label to the outside of the container. On the packing slip (or a piece of paper, if packing slip is unavailable) please write out the exchange you are requesting and place it inside the package.</li><li>The box is able be taken to anywhere they will perform a UPS pickup or any standard UPS store.</li><li>All shipments being returned will come back to us via standard ground shipping (1-5 business days dependent on location according to the UPS website)</li><li>Once received your order is guaranteed to be processed on our end within 7-10 business days and the exchange will be sent back out via UPS Ground Shipping (1-5 Business Days dependent on location according to the UPS website). If you are curious to know the status of your exchange please contact our customer service department via email - <a href="mailto:cs@unitedspb.com">cs@unitedspb.com</a> or call <a href="tel:1-800-233-6956">800-233-6956</a> and we'll gladly assist you!</li></ol><p class="subtextdisclaimer"><span style="font-size: small;"><em>*Please Note That Approval of the Exchange will be Dependent Upon Available Inventory of the Product in Question*</em></span></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.pImageListS